            <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-100 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-6 group-hover:bg-emerald-700 group-hover:text-white transition-colors" aria-hidden="true">ðŸŒ</div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-emerald-950 mb-3">Truly remote â€” not remote-ish</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-emerald-800/80 font-medium leading-relaxed">We have never had an office and never will. Our team spans 14 time zones. Async communication is how we actually work, not an afterthought. You will have genuine flexibility to build a life around work, not the other way.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-cream-50 border border-emerald-100 rounded-3xl p-8 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl hover:border-emerald-200 transition-all duration-300 relative overflow-hidden group">
            <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-700 to-emerald-500 scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 origin-left transition-transform duration-500" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-100 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-6 group-hover:bg-emerald-700 group-hover:text-white transition-colors" aria-hidden="true">ðŸ“ˆ</div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-emerald-950 mb-3">Early-stage leverage</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-emerald-800/80 font-medium leading-relaxed">We are still small enough that each person shapes the product and culture meaningfully. If you have an idea and build a case for it, it gets heard. Bureaucracy has not arrived yet and we intend to keep it that way.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-cream-50 border border-emerald-100 rounded-3xl p-8 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl hover:border-emerald-200 transition-all duration-300 relative overflow-hidden group">
            <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-700 to-emerald-500 scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 origin-left transition-transform duration-500" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-100 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-6 group-hover:bg-emerald-700 group-hover:text-white transition-colors" aria-hidden="true">ðŸ’š</div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-emerald-950 mb-3">Values without performance</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-emerald-800/80 font-medium leading-relaxed">We are faith-aware but not performative. Prayer times are respected. Ramadan hours are adjusted. Eid is a holiday without you needing to negotiate it. We do not need to be reminded because we care about the same things you do.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-cream-50 border border-emerald-100 rounded-3xl p-8 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl hover:border-emerald-200 transition-all duration-300 relative overflow-hidden group">
            <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-700 to-emerald-500 scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 origin-left transition-transform duration-500" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-100 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-6 group-hover:bg-emerald-700 group-hover:text-white transition-colors" aria-hidden="true">ðŸ“š</div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-emerald-950 mb-3">Learning budget, no strings</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-emerald-800/80 font-medium leading-relaxed">Every full-time team member receives an annual learning budget to spend on courses, books, conferences, or tools. No approval forms. No pre-approved list. We trust you to invest in yourself â€” and by extension, us.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-cream-50 border border-emerald-100 rounded-3xl p-8 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl hover:border-emerald-200 transition-all duration-300 relative overflow-hidden group">
            <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-700 to-emerald-500 scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 origin-left transition-transform duration-500" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-100 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-6 group-hover:bg-emerald-700 group-hover:text-white transition-colors" aria-hidden="true">ðŸ›¡ï¸</div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-emerald-950 mb-3">Honest about what we are not</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-emerald-800/80 font-medium leading-relaxed">We are not a high-growth VC-backed startup chasing an exit. We grow at a pace that lets us serve families well. If you want rocket-ship scale above all else, we are probably not the right fit â€” and we would rather tell you now.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Section>

    <Section height={400} class="py-12 md:py-24 lg:py-32 bg-emerald-950 relative overflow-hidden text-center">
      <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[800px] h-[800px] bg-amber-500/5 rounded-full blur-[100px] pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="absolute top-[-10%] right-[-5%] w-[400px] h-[400px] border border-white/5 rounded-full pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 relative z-10">
        <span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-amber-400 block mb-8">Our North Star</span>
        
        <p class="font-serif text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-medium italic text-white leading-tight tracking-tight mb-16 text-balance mx-auto">
          Every Muslim child in the world growing up with a <strong class="text-amber-400 not-italic font-bold">genuine love for the Quran</strong> â€” not a fear of it.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3 lg:gap-4">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-50 backdrop-blur-sm">
            <span class="text-lg" aria-hidden="true">ðŸ§ </span> Empathy-led teaching
          </div>
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-50 backdrop-blur-sm">
            <span class="text-lg" aria-hidden="true">ðŸ›¡ï¸</span> Zero financial risk
          </div>
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-50 backdrop-blur-sm">
            <span class="text-lg" aria-hidden="true">ðŸ“Š</span> Full transparency
          </div>
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-50 backdrop-blur-sm">
            <span class="text-lg" aria-hidden="true">ðŸŒ</span> 22 countries and growing
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Section>

    <Section height={900} class="py-12 md:py-24 bg-cream-50" id="open-roles">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="mb-16">
          <span class="text-xs font-black tracking-widest uppercase text-emerald-700 block mb-3">Open Roles</span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-emerald-950 mb-4 tracking-tight">Find your <em class="font-serif italic text-emerald-700 font-medium">place on the team.</em></h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-emerald-900/80 font-medium">All roles are fully remote unless stated. We welcome applications from anywhere in the world.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-[280px_1fr] gap-12 items-start">
          
          <div class="lg:sticky lg:top-32">
            <div class="text-sm font-bold text-emerald-950 mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider">Filter by department</div>
            <div class="space-y-2 mb-8">
              <button class="w-full flex items-center justify-between px-4 py-3 rounded-xl text-sm font-bold transition-all duration-300 rf active bg-emerald-700 text-white border border-emerald-700 shadow-md" data-dept="all">
                <span>All roles</span>
                <span class="rf-count px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/20 text-white text-xs border-transparent border">8</span>
              </button>
              <button class="w-full flex items-center justify-between px-4 py-3 rounded-xl text-sm font-bold transition-all duration-300 rf bg-transparent text-emerald-900/70 border border-transparent hover:bg-emerald-50 hover:text-emerald-950" data-dept="teaching">
                <span>Teaching</span>
                <span class="rf-count px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white border border-emerald-100 text-emerald-900/50 text-xs">3</span>
              </button>
              <button class="w-full flex items-center justify-between px-4 py-3 rounded-xl text-sm font-bold transition-all duration-300 rf bg-transparent text-emerald-900/70 border border-transparent hover:bg-emerald-50 hover:text-emerald-950" data-dept="product">
                <span>Product & Tech</span>
                <span class="rf-count px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white border border-emerald-100 text-emerald-900/50 text-xs">2</span>
              </button>
              <button class="w-full flex items-center justify-between px-4 py-3 rounded-xl text-sm font-bold transition-all duration-300 rf bg-transparent text-emerald-900/70 border border-transparent hover:bg-emerald-50 hover:text-emerald-950" data-dept="operations">
                <span>Operations</span>
                <span class="rf-count px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white border border-emerald-100 text-emerald-900/50 text-xs">2</span>
              </button>
              <button class="w-full flex items-center justify-between px-4 py-3 rounded-xl text-sm font-bold transition-all duration-300 rf bg-transparent text-emerald-900/70 border border-transparent hover:bg-emerald-50 hover:text-emerald-950" data-dept="marketing">
                <span>Marketing</span>
                <span class="rf-count px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white border border-emerald-100 text-emerald-900/50 text-xs">1</span>
              </button>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white border border-emerald-100 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm">
              <h4 class="font-bold text-emerald-950 text-sm mb-2">Don't see your role?</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-emerald-800/70 font-medium leading-relaxed mb-4">We hire for attitude and mission-fit before we hire for a specific role. If Quranific sounds like home, reach out anyway.</p>
              <a href="mailto:careers@quranific.com" class="block text-center px-4 py-3 bg-emerald-700 text-white text-sm font-bold rounded-xl hover:bg-emerald-900 transition-colors shadow-sm">Send an open application</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-4" id="roles-list">
            
            <div class="role-card bg-white border border-emerald-100 rounded-3xl p-8 cursor-pointer hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-emerald-200 transition-all duration-300 relative overflow-hidden group" data-dept="product">
              <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-1 bg-amber-500 scale-y-0 group-hover:scale-y-100 origin-bottom transition-transform duration-300" aria-hidden="true"></div>
              <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-start justify-between gap-4 mb-4">
                <div>
                  <h3 class="role-title text-xl font-bold text-emerald-950 mb-1.5">Senior Full-Stack Engineer</h3>
                  <div class="text-xs font-bold text-emerald-700 uppercase tracking-wider">Product & Tech</div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 shrink-0">
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 text-xs font-bold rounded-full">Full-time</span>
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-cream-50 border border-emerald-100 text-emerald-900/60 text-xs font-bold rounded-full">Remote</span>
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 text-amber-600 text-xs font-bold rounded-full">New</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-emerald-800/80 font-medium leading-relaxed mb-6">We are rebuilding our core platform on Astro 5 and Svelte 5. You will own the funnel experience, teacher-parent reporting pipeline, and our Cloudflare Workers architecture. You will be the third engineer on a product used by 3,200 families daily.</p>
              <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center justify-between gap-4 pt-5 border-t border-emerald-50">
                <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 sm:gap-4 text-sm font-medium text-emerald-900/60">
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5" aria-hidden="true"><span class="text-lg">ðŸ’°</span> $90â€“120k</div>
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-200"></span> Astro Â· Svelte</div>
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-200"></span> 3â€“5 yrs exp.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="text-emerald-700 font-bold text-sm flex items-center gap-1.5 group-hover:gap-3 transition-all duration-300">Apply now â†’</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="role-card bg-white border border-emerald-100 rounded-3xl p-8 cursor-pointer hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-emerald-200 transition-all duration-300 relative overflow-hidden group" data-dept="product">
              <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-1 bg-amber-500 scale-y-0 group-hover:scale-y-100 origin-bottom transition-transform duration-300" aria-hidden="true"></div>
              <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-start justify-between gap-4 mb-4">
                <div>
                  <h3 class="role-title text-xl font-bold text-emerald-950 mb-1.5">Product Designer â€” UX Lead</h3>
                  <div class="text-xs font-bold text-emerald-700 uppercase tracking-wider">Product & Tech</div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 shrink-0">
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 text-xs font-bold rounded-full">Full-time</span>
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-cream-50 border border-emerald-100 text-emerald-900/60 text-xs font-bold rounded-full">Remote</span>
                </div>
              </div>
