          <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-700 animate-pulse" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          Remote Â· Mission-driven Â· Hiring now
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-emerald-950 mb-6 tracking-tight leading-tight">
          Still reading?<br/>
          That means <em class="font-serif italic text-emerald-700 font-medium">this is for you.</em>
        </h2>
        
        <p class="text-lg lg:text-xl text-emerald-900/80 font-medium mb-10 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          The people who thrive at Quranific are the ones who felt something reading this page â€” not just interest in a job, but recognition of a problem they have personally felt. If that is you, we want to hear from you.
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <Button href="#open-roles" variant="primary" class="w-full sm:w-auto px-10 py-5 text-lg">
            See Open Roles
          </Button>
          <Button href="mailto:careers@quranific.com" variant="ghost" class="w-full sm:w-auto px-10 py-5 text-lg">
            Send open application
          </Button>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-900/50">We respond to every application within 5 working days. No exceptions.</p>
      </div>
